															<span class="description">Array of arguments for inserting a new comment. <ul class="param-hash"><li><b>'comment_agent'</b><br /><i><span class='type'>(string)</span></i> The HTTP user agent of the &lt;code&gt;$comment_author&lt;/code&gt; when the comment was submitted. Default empty. </li>
