<li><b>'comment_author_url'</b><br /><i><span class='type'>(string)</span></i> The URL address of the &lt;code&gt;$comment_author&lt;/code&gt;. Default empty. </li>
<li><b>'comment_content'</b><br /><i><span class='type'>(string)</span></i> The content of the comment. Default empty. </li>
<li><b>'comment_date'</b><br /><i><span class='type'>(string)</span></i> The date the comment was submitted. To set the date manually, &lt;code&gt;$comment_date_gmt&lt;/code&gt; must also be specified. Default is the current time. </li>
