<li><b>'comment_post_ID'</b><br /><i><span class='type'>(int)</span></i> ID of the post that relates to the comment, if any. Default empty. </li>
<li><b>'comment_type'</b><br /><i><span class='type'>(string)</span></i> Comment type. Default empty. </li>
<li><b>'user_id'</b><br /><i><span class='type'>(int)</span></i> ID of the user who submitted the comment. Default 0.</li>
